ormal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用dybala或者icardi仲好la"},{"pid":"3fb40ec560055c07ff605bcadb78f1c3c95c19ce","tid":493343,"uid":9807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲都決賽腳軟<br />\n同一場單刀都唔入<br />\n何況罰球？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能次次入到決賽都輸，有心理陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a31c04e44477b897860735706ceba5a8213608","tid":493343,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"馬勒當拿私下教佢(鳩UP)"},{"pid":"6e385f2e5b871fa6e23e819888488d5eb8a0f926","tid":493343,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"下年關鍵時候咪又係打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee282dc0720278601b6246e1ffe5915d798ad79","tid":493343,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲都決賽腳軟<br />\n同一場單刀都唔入<br />\n何況罰球？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係教練<br />\n入到決賽就將佢同斜恩連後備名單都唔入<br />\n兩個都係決賽殺手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過今年過到分組賽先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37d73b6f0e9ac1e81648d62cb5b3a83d60b0638","tid":493343,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13391bdfef9d9afda6cba922d667179697280620","tid":493343,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b61cd5c56f3055f2906d9218f1dd0eb92e064380","tid":493343,"uid":35176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy